               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Bandlet of Righteousness, ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡; Prayer in Amharic</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="43r"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT2246salotz"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ‎‎ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ዘጸሐፋ፡ አብሮኮሮስ፡ ረድአ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎‎ጸሎት፡ ዘጸለየት፡ ባቲ፡ አመ፡ ፳ወ፩ ለሰኔ፡ በደብረ፡ ጎልጎታ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="43r" to="58r"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT1758Lefafa"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                        <locus from="43r" to="44r"/>
                        <title>Prayer for the momebannt of the agony of death, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፃዕረ፡ ሞት።</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፃዕረ፡ ሞት፡ ድቃስ፡ በትሮን ‎‎ምጕያዮን፡ ከዋስ፡ ቄርላዎስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                        <locus from="44r" to="47v"/>
                        <title>Prayer for Cleansing from Sin, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መንጽሔ፡ ኃጢአት።</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መንጽሔ፡ ኃጢአት፡ ለትንጻሕ፡ ‎‎እምድር፡ በከመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አንጻሕኮ፡ ለአቡነ፡ አዳም፡ ከመ፡ ‎clፈጠሮ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                        <locus from="47v" to="48v"/>
                        <title>Prayer for Burial, ጸሎት፡ ግብዓተ፡ መሬት።</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ በል፡ ጸሎት፡ ግብዓተ፡ መሬት፡ ኃደግናከ፡ ወአግባዕናከ፡ ‎‎ውስተ፡ መሬት፡ ኀበ፡ ዘቀዳሜ፡ ፍጥረትከ፡ ተዘከር፡ ኃጢአተነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4">
                        <locus from="48v" to="49v"/>
                        <title>Asmat Prayer of the Trinity for Protection of the Soul</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ‎በስመ፡ በል፡ ፩ ስ፡ መሰብኤል፡ ፩ስሙ፡ ብርሃናኤል፡ ፩ስ፤ ድምናኤል፡ ‎‎<gap reason="omitted"/> እሉ፡ አስማት፡ ዓቃቢያኒሃ፡ ለነፍስ፡‎
                  </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5">
                        <locus from="49v" to="50v"/>
                        <title>Benefits of Reading the Bandlet of Righteouness</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስ፡ በል፡ እነግረክሙ፡ አኃውየ፡ እለ፡ ትትአመኑ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ልፋፈ፡ ‎‎ጽድቅ፡ ዘወሀባ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.6">
                        <locus from="50v" to="53v"/>
                        <title>Prayers for the journey to heaven, ጸሎት፡ ዘመንገደ፡ ሰማይ፡</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ በል፡ ዘመንገደ፡ ሰማይ፡ ከመ፡ ኢያዕቅፍዋ፡ መላእክተ፡ ‎‎ጽልመት፡ ለነፍስየ፡ በኤልደን፡ ስመ፡ መንበርከ<gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                        <note>First prayer (<locus target="#50v #51r"/>),
                    second prayer (<locus target="#51r #51v"/>),
                    third prayer (<locus target="#51v"/>),
                    ‎fourth prayer (<locus target="#51v #52r"/>),
                    fifth prayer (<locus target="#52r #52v"/>),
                    sixth prayer (<locus target="#52v #‎‎53r"/>),
                    seventh prayer (<locus target="#53r #53v"/>)‎</note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.7">
                        <locus from="53v" to="54v"/>
                        <title>Homily on the Suffering of Our Lord by Mary Magdalene, Salome, and Elizabeth, ዜና፡ ሕማማቲሁ፡ ለእግዚአነ።</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በሰመ፡ አብ፡ ብ፡ ዜና፡ ሕማማቲሁ፡ ለእግዚአነ፡ ኢየሱስ ክርስቶስ፡ ‎‎ዘከሠተ፡ ሎን፡ ለሰላስ፡ አንስት፡ እለ፡ ይሰመያ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.8">
                        <locus from="54v" to="58r"/>
                        <title>Asmat Prayers of Our Lord given to the Apostles</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ወተስእልዎ፡ አርዳኢሁ፡ ለእግዚአነ፡ ‎‎ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ይቤልዎ፡ ክስት፡ ለነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                     </msItem>

                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="59v" to="60r"/>
                    <title>Prayer in Amharic, written according to the formula of the Layman’s prayer, <foreign xml:lang="am">አዳምን፡ ከሲኦል፡ ኖኅን፡ ከማየ፡ አይኅ።</foreign> “As you saved Adam from Sheol, Solomon from the mouth of the lions, Israel from Pharoah, Job from his wound, George from the seventy kings, the apostles from the hand of unbelievers, Ethiopians from the yoke of Italians,. . .save me, your servant<gap reason="omitted"/> .”</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="am">
                      ‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወል፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> አዳምን፡ ከሲኦል፡ ሰሎሞንን፡ ከአፈ፡ አናብስት፡ ‎‎እስራኤልን፡ ከፈርኦን፡ ኢዮብን፡ ከቁስል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስን፡ ከሰባ፡ ‎‎ነገሥታት፡ ሐዋርያትን፡ ከእደ፡ አላውያን፡ ኢትዮጵያን፡ ከኢጣልያን፡ ‎‎ቀ[ን]በር፡ ያወጣህ<gap reason="omitted"/> ‎
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
